{"sha": "39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjM5ZGRiZWI4NzQ3MDA3MTExM2QwM2ZhN2RmYzM0MTY0MTgwYzc2ZDY=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Pietro Albini", "email": "pietro@pietroalbini.org", "date": "2019-12-11T10:06:40Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Pietro Albini", "email": "pietro@pietroalbini.org", "date": "2019-12-30T13:56:51Z"}, "message": "ci: fix wrong sysroot in macos 10.15 onwards\n\nIn their infinite wisdom, Apple decided that (starting from macOS 10.15\nonwards) /usr/include is not the location we should all search in for\nour beloved C headers. Instead, we should look inside the extremely\nintuitive and easily guessable new path:\n\n/Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Platforms/MacOSX.platform/Developer/SDKs/MacOSX.sdk/usr/include\n\nBecause why not.", "tree": {"sha": "b947d237aa8aadabdf2b6420df80eb15269cb836", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/b947d237aa8aadabdf2b6420df80eb15269cb836"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": true, "reason": "valid", "signature": "-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\niQIzBAABCAAdFiEE1JbYPtLJAsc22U9xPgar6Auq8ZwFAl4KAiMACgkQPgar6Auq\n8Zzyuw//cm/SuuNEvN4pYppGUoDj4laJ54Rf0HZ3kY3gn85ITuJqlkqj1M+4jEj2\nJjaTpTRx8E882KnuVSqGTVTDoLoNr2jMKscNUvBGcjy7MYc5rXcqWfpJxNNXlzbb\nMghwQTdu+RL+OewrBFei1mvaXXdngq9DGNeMOkg1tL5JJVzBDDw7IDoe9EsG/24a\nPn7YC2y05umeiqvTpRT1+aG0W0/nVG4guhXO3QCpSsJJKxT5aS1onAgdgGPT6nw+\nCErvaxd2wUENmhOJbGWN8N8kQSnPf6ixL1DT7E0BE0Z9rIUmYaY3zh7eggoYFsZX\ne6JWhh0k2Rez2fuTYsLQLXvEU9sfJXMHz0KyZ8ytTA9iW8GpIScYxI/uhp3poqVl\nzAygE0uiCve5YL1+E3UUr9DELEW3jBe+Zg39OUyWIUDt3XutEE1lMRa8zBRJ5SOg\n31KHa8IsHng3QNeH4YXP3BJK0pXw2rVKGe2CH5QHC55Go9gBbxssIZ+xCd+UNOZa\nruBCIbI2Cqm6JJcHqib+xWx/fZBxUpS2O6gW7Ph3DPhyZ72M3DeyYGQGpsBLCZn3\ncb9rBOyd1i/iMlP97ILYQSDEIaLCjy9Y4tjkpx36xBK1Z7fq/fo2ZNm3+YQiRiUA\nORYPzU7a/T4Q30oBLE/zJt+b/8FbvlSR7YvuTBf8mILrOf1MqWU=\n=rFP6\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----", "payload": "tree b947d237aa8aadabdf2b6420df80eb15269cb836\nparent 846d386b4d84faa6c5f373d0f608e859239465e8\nauthor Pietro Albini <pietro@pietroalbini.org> 1576058800 +0100\ncommitter Pietro Albini <pietro@pietroalbini.org> 1577714211 +0100\n\nci: fix wrong sysroot in macos 10.15 onwards\n\nIn their infinite wisdom, Apple decided that (starting from macOS 10.15\nonwards) /usr/include is not the location we should all search in for\nour beloved C headers. Instead, we should look inside the extremely\nintuitive and easily guessable new path:\n\n/Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Platforms/MacOSX.platform/Developer/SDKs/MacOSX.sdk/usr/include\n\nBecause why not.\n"}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6/comments", "author": {"login": "pietroalbini", "id": 2299951, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIyOTk5NTE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2299951?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini", "html_url": "https://github.com/pietroalbini", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "committer": {"login": "pietroalbini", "id": 2299951, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIyOTk5NTE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2299951?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini", "html_url": "https://github.com/pietroalbini", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pietroalbini/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "parents": [{"sha": "846d386b4d84faa6c5f373d0f608e859239465e8", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/846d386b4d84faa6c5f373d0f608e859239465e8", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/846d386b4d84faa6c5f373d0f608e859239465e8"}], "stats": {"total": 9, "additions": 9, "deletions": 0}, "files": [{"sha": "e16a4814197b31159b53040c4c950b59d222cf18", "filename": "src/ci/scripts/install-clang.sh", "status": "modified", "additions": 9, "deletions": 0, "changes": 9, "blob_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6/src%2Fci%2Fscripts%2Finstall-clang.sh", "raw_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/raw/39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6/src%2Fci%2Fscripts%2Finstall-clang.sh", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/contents/src%2Fci%2Fscripts%2Finstall-clang.sh?ref=39ddbeb87470071113d03fa7dfc34164180c76d6", "patch": "@@ -14,6 +14,15 @@ if isMacOS; then\n     ciCommandSetEnv CC \"$(pwd)/clang+llvm-9.0.0-x86_64-darwin-apple/bin/clang\"\n     ciCommandSetEnv CXX \"$(pwd)/clang+llvm-9.0.0-x86_64-darwin-apple/bin/clang++\"\n \n+    # macOS 10.15 onwards doesn't have libraries in /usr/include anymore: those\n+    # are now located deep into the filesystem, under Xcode's own files. The\n+    # native clang is configured to use the correct path, but our custom one\n+    # doesn't. This sets the SDKROOT environment variable to the SDK so that\n+    # our own clang can figure out the correct include path on its own.\n+    if ! [[ -d \"/usr/include\" ]]; then\n+        ciCommandSetEnv SDKROOT \"$(xcrun --sdk macosx --show-sdk-path)\"\n+    fi\n+\n     # Configure `AR` specifically so rustbuild doesn't try to infer it as\n     # `clang-ar` by accident.\n     ciCommandSetEnv AR \"ar\""}]}